steps.name: Given I am logged in to the app
And I tap on product title "Sauce Labs Onesie"

Then I should be navigated to product details screen with title "Sauce Labs Onesie", price "$7.99" and description "Rib snap infant onesie for the junior automation engineer in development. Reinforced 3-snap bottom closure, two-needle hemmed sleeved and bottom won't unravel."
And I should be able to log out of the app
